{"tid":776763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於戰鬥民族","createTime":"2018-08-12T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T11:56:16.000Z","uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39d23b4aea66081bf5a8e3209f2345f69057e1f7","tid":776763,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"近來常吹戰鬥民族風<br />\n說戰鬥民族，好好打云云<br />\n經查<br />\n俄羅斯聯邦只正式打過場內戰，對手是車臣，好多年攻入格羅茲尼慘勝<br />\n當年報紙標題：傷心車臣，莫斯科慘勝。<br />\n蘇聯自己落手打既仗亦唔多<br />\n對芬蘭一場，芬蘭勝<br />\n對阿富汗一場，阿富汗勝<br />\n或許之所以要吹戰鬥民族，只因不常戰鬥，也少贏"},{"pid":"edd6a06ca63afef4041340ee0ce8b50d8c1e1ae5","tid":776763,"uid":70760,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"對住香港人 台仔都變左撒亞人"},{"pid":"6303251ccd8a61e7f5ed9f3340853297f126fc53","tid":776763,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"樓主唔講贏嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a76321f839075abcb36a6f4752f47600a47b9d4","tid":776763,"uid":66928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"其實係咪好多人都覺得，第二次世界大戰係英美打贏德國，並唔係俄國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea28150e25ba76b17e3a26451e5dfe6652e14fb4","tid":776763,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a76321f839075abcb36a6f4752f47600a47b9d4","tid":776763,"uid":66928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"其實係咪好多人都覺得，第二次世界大戰係英美打贏德國，並唔係俄國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"無租借法案美國源源不絕運物資比蘇聯，打輸唔敢講，但打赢就難d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2fe8393d28b8dad146d2f09ec21789aec4d751","tid":776763,"uid":66928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea28150e25ba76b17e3a26451e5dfe6652e14fb4","tid":776763,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pi